sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant COORD as Coordinator
    participant CB as Circuit Breaker
    participant HC as Health Prober
    participant DN as Decoder Node
    participant PM as Prometheus
    participant HPA as K8s Autoscaler

    loop Every 10s
        HC->>DN: GET /health
        alt Healthy
            DN-->>HC: 200 OK
            HC->>CB: recordSuccess()
            CB->>CB: CLOSED (normal)
        else Unhealthy or timeout
            DN--xHC: failure
            HC->>CB: recordFailure()
            CB->>CB: OPEN (skip node)
            Note over CB: After cooldown → HALF-OPEN
            CB->>DN: probe request
            alt recovered
                DN-->>CB: 200 OK
                CB->>CB: CLOSED
            else still down
                CB->>CB: OPEN again
            end
        end
        HC->>COORD: Update pool registry
    end

    COORD-->>PM: Pool metrics (size, healthy, circuit-breakers)
    DN-->>PM: Node metrics (utilization, latency, QPS)
    PM-->>HPA: Metrics (CPU, GPU, latency, QPS)
    HPA->>DN: Scale up / down replicas
